pkgdepR object

Source: R/S3methods.R
is.pkgdepR.Rd

An internal generic function. Methods for is.pkgdepR should only return TRUE if the class is pkgdepR.

Usage

is.pkgdepR(x)

Arguments

x

Object to be tested.

Value

Boolean. TRUE when x is of class pkgdepR.
